\n嗰邊d A等於dse 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1ce9cc2fb53b966ac20fc3dfd2c60a3af4f6ce69","tid":403261,"uid":144580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實講，呢d科，真係算廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10個有8個香港人讀呢d科都係咁嘅grade</blockquote><br />\n 但總有人考唔到迦嘛 巴打你考到你咪叻咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰邊d A等於dse 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/170819_b04c6d723b5f538326eeda963622e5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F170819_b04c6d723b5f538326eeda963622e5d2.jpg&h=7cdf3175&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87aa30489264d42f8d2ab343235b50a7b16b2390","tid":403261,"uid":144580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ielts得7都好意思幫人補英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg&h=0e51a747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都差不多5* 又有幾多人拎到？"},{"pid":"59afc3b5346e1cea0baea9fbe970f79c6744dc7b","tid":403261,"uid":126510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ielts得7都好意思幫人補英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg&h=0e51a747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都差不多5* 又有幾多人拎到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個對照之前畀人屌到飛起<br />\n佢係捉12年個批dse雞去考ielts<br />\ndse人地就prep足3年，直接影響前途<br />\nielts人地3日preparation都唔知有無，輸贏都無所謂，成個考試心態都唔同<br />\n<br />\n事實上你如果真係兩個都考過<br />\n就會知ielts band 7 大概係 <br />\n比較高分既 lv4<br />\n運氣好可能有5<br />\n但無咩可能5*"},{"pid":"3f6b18a0b80f0c9a532058352a79b5acf00e0a16","tid":403261,"uid":38528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"樓主咪理佢地啦<br />\nDSE 5=冇資格教,垃圾  5*/5**,唔識教都冇用,唔明學生唔明D咩<br />\nielts 7 =垃圾,基本要求, 8=垃圾,speaking幾多?又唔係native"},{"pid":"1a8518a55759754bb8c104ede49daec3abfddb74","tid":403261,"uid":126897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"反而想知點解A* A* AA 要入KCL <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d6eec30d3fec4dc9bbda9545a98c1df79a8b38","tid":403261,"uid":60115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ielts得7都好意思幫人補英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg&h=0e51a747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都差不多5* 又有幾多人拎到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個對照之前畀人屌到飛起<br />\n佢係捉12年個批dse雞去考ielts<br />\ndse人地就prep足3年，直接影響前途<br />\nielts人地3日preparation都唔知有無，輸贏都無所謂，成個考試心態都唔同<br />\n<br />\n事實上你如果真係兩個都考過<br />\n就會知ielts band 7 大概係 <br />\n比較高分既 lv4<br />\n運氣好可能有5<br />\n但無咩可能5*</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n ielts7=5* 真係傻佬先信"},{"pid":"008a4f3de9949b0d5273b4565372797dc33dab73","tid":403261,"uid":126897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實講，呢d科，真係算廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10個有8個香港人讀呢d科都係咁嘅grade</blockquote><br />\n 但總有人考唔到迦嘛 巴打你考到你咪叻咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰邊d A等於dse 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/170819_b04c6d723b5f538326eeda963622e5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F170819_b04c6d723b5f538326eeda963622e5d2.jpg&h=7cdf3175&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n原本以為5** 係A*, 5*係A, 5 係B ... 咁如此類推. 原來唔係. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c14dceac14b978c6c2d7d1e144f837b73239a6","tid":403261,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"13faa945a20906529a54ac720c38c3bb840961e7","tid":403261,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ielts得7都好意思幫人補英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F171123_36e87f145f310b8b28e9c33de0c505ec.jpg&h=0e51a747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都差不多5* 又有幾多人拎到？</blockquote><br />\n英文得5 同人補咩習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有 gce中文A* 是垃圾科<br />\n<br />\n數學A* 亦無大用<br />\n<br />\n反而gce a level英文考到A* 就輾壓絕大部分香港考生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edb31430f656d4dbd343fd96a004d16ad20b988","tid":403261,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實講，呢d科，真係算廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10個有8個香港人讀呢d科都係咁嘅grade</blockquote><br />\n 但總有人考唔到迦嘛 巴打你考到你咪叻咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰邊d A等於dse 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/170819_b04c6d723b5f538326eeda963622e5d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F170819_b04c6d723b5f538326eeda963622e5d2.jpg&h=7cdf3175&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個係英國個承認程度，唔係難度分嚟，唔好蝦我唔識嘢，小弟以前都係英國AL 4A<br />\n數學份卷根本淺過dse好多，操都唔使操，就咁平時上吓堂交吓功課就有A<br />\n嗰陣我好似78-9%就有A, 香港要拎5*要接近90%, 根本d競爭對手都唔同level<br />\n<br />\n你如果係4科文科都有A我就話你有料到</blockquote><br />\nhkal 既理科 gce既文科 真係絕配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c046bd2e2ff723ee3ee76b51342d3805d338f2e","tid":403261,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35bfb620ce85c2a4dbb584165c240b3c0ac6a207","tid":403261,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:43:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03b9ac243d0c5d7fefbb769864cc12099c46ca60","tid":403261,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而想知點解A* A* AA 要入KCL <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰邊d A好撚濫<br />\n個個香港人/大陸狗都喺嗰邊屈鬼仔(只限數/phy)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔夠薑同人鬥history/eng lit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入得oxbridge通常要最top嗰d A, 唔係求其踩住條邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔好咁膚淺<br />\n<br />\n公平d 講，香港人同鬼仔 考eng lit同 history雖然會輸， 但又未至於太肉酸<br />\n<br />\n鬼仔同香港人一齊考中國文學同中國歷史， 鬼仔仲唔炒到飛起？<br />\n<br />\n數理科算係比較中立既科， 英國美國攪咁耐學生平均數理能力仲係